{"tid":328682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【明報A1】英國檔案：李嘉誠1989年有意入英藉","createTime":"2017-07-19T18:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T18:28:12.000Z","uid":5195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9e21290453491503d6cd776150f404cb8c913db","tid":328682,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:14:41.000Z","msg":"明報A1搶先睇<br />\n【密檔揭秘】根據英國國家檔案館新一批解封的檔案，時任基本法起草委員會委員、香港首席富商李嘉誠，1989年3月曾與當時的英國首相戴卓爾夫人見面，會議紀綠顯示她知悉李「有興趣取得英國公民資格（Mr. Li's interest in acquiring British citizenship）」，並會責成內政大臣與他進一步商討。文件並披露，李嘉誠希望英國政府運用酌情權，令部分香港資金可在英國安家落戶&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/20229250_1496205843772879_5126171995769824749_n.jpg?oh=00c7376fe8026adcacb4888d589cc907&amp;oe=5A0053C7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F20229250_1496205843772879_5126171995769824749_n.jpg%3Foh%3D00c7376fe8026adcacb4888d589cc907%26oe%3D5A0053C7&h=abc0dff5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f9bcbfc2c3e0dbc00ba1a4f3c336401e7d174bb8","tid":328682,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"入加拿大籍好過啦"},{"pid":"ba219d07261869ae2e390ba197c261a98b9d8b3b","tid":328682,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:20:15.000Z","msg":"佢而家乜野籍"},{"pid":"e0af5470c67d8e8b1ae8ae4c9094f724737a6c29","tid":328682,"uid":93986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:20:51.000Z","msg":"口講為國家貢獻<br />\n實際搵夠大陸人錢再走佬<br />\n誠仔真係唔會死錯人"},{"pid":"79123d0d1fcbb18b3381e8617a5c2619803b6e7a","tid":328682,"uid":16731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T18:28:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}